OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FThe family of the groundbreaking ITV
OL,7,Fjournalist Roger Cook, who was behind
OL,8,Fthe long-running "The Cook Report"
OL,9,Fseries, have paid tribute to him,
OL,10,Fafter he passed away at the weekend at
OL,11,Fthe age of 83.
OL,13,FHe had been treated at the Royal
OL,14,FUnited Hospitals Bath for three weeks
OL,15,Fwhere he was found to have a cancerous
OL,16,Ftumour at the base of his spine.
OL,18,FHe was once described as the "bravest
OL,19,F- and most beaten up" journalist in
OL,20,FBritain.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
