OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FIn a statement his family said: "It is
OL,7,Fwith great sadness that we announce
OL,8,Fthe passing of Roger Cook, who died
OL,9,Fpeacefully on Saturday after a short
OL,10,Fillness.
OL,12,F"Alongside a distinguished and award
OL,13,Fwinning career in journalism, Roger
OL,14,Fwas first and foremost a beloved
OL,15,Fhusband and father.
OL,17,F"He will be deeply missed by all of
OL,18,Fus, and we ask for privacy as we
OL,19,Fnavigate this difficult loss".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
