OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FCook hosted "The Cook Report", the
OL,7,Ffamous ITV investigative news and
OL,8,Fcurrent affairs series. It was
OL,9,Fproduced by Central Independent
OL,10,FTelevision in Birmingham and
OL,11,FNottingham.
OL,13,FHe joined ITV in 1985 and his
OL,14,Feponymous "The Cook Report" ran for 16
OL,15,Fseries with more than 120 episodes.
OL,17,FHe became known for his groundbreaking
OL,18,Fpursuit of wrongdoing as he pursued
OL,19,Fcriminals, con-men and corrupt
OL,20,Fofficials.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
