PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FThe show exposed child pornography,
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland protection rackets,
OL,8,Fbaby trading in Brazil, the tainted
OL,9,Fblood scandal and the illicit ivory
OL,10,Ftrade.
OL,12,FHe also investigated illegal
OL,13,Fimmigration, war criminals in Bosnia
OL,14,Fand those behind 9/11 and other
OL,15,Fterrorist plots, as well as exposing
OL,16,Fthe Russian black market in weapons-
OL,17,Fgrade plutonium.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
