PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FHe was injured many times in the
OL,7,Fcourse of exposing wrongdoing, for
OL,8,Fwhat was the most popular current
OL,9,Faffairs programme on television at the
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FUp to 12 million people tuned into his
OL,13,Fprogramme, which won 11 national and
OL,14,Finternational awards and a BAFTA
OL,15,Fspecial award for Cook in 1997.
OL,17,FA number of his programmes were
OL,18,Ffollowed by successful police
OL,19,Fprosecutions or major changes in the
OL,20,Flaw.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
