OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FRoger Cook was born in New Zealand but
OL,7,Fmoved to Australia as a child.
OL,9,FHe began his career as a reporter and
OL,10,Fnewsreader with the Australian
OL,11,FBroadcasting Corporation, and moved to
OL,12,Fthe UK in 1968, where he worked for
OL,13,Fthe BBC, initially on the World at
OL,14,FOne, PM, Nationwide and Newsnight.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
