PN,34707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FHe created the investigative programme
OL,7,FCheckpoint for Radio 4 in 1973,
OL,8,Fexposing con men, major criminals and
OL,9,Fofficial incompetence ` a programme
OL,10,Fthat saw him beaten with an iron bar
OL,11,Fby an art dealer in Brighton selling
OL,12,Ffake antiques. He broke three ribs.
OL,14,FIn 1985 he moved to ITV to launch the
OL,15,F"Cook Report" in Birmingham for
OL,16,FCentral TV.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
