PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FThe series ran until 1999. In 2007, he
OL,7,Freturned to the screen with a 90
OL,8,Fminute special programme which
OL,9,Frevisited and updated some of his
OL,10,Fearlier groundbreaking stories.
OL,12,FHe leaves his wife Frances, and
OL,13,Fdaughter Belinda.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
