CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,FIn a statement, ITV said: "In a career
OL,7,Fspanning an incredible five decades,
OL,8,FRoger Cook's groundbreaking approach
OL,9,Fto investigative journalism made him
OL,10,Fone of broadcasting's most trusted and
OL,11,Frespected figures.
OL,13,F"On his eponymous current affairs
OL,14,Fprogramme, The Cook Report, Roger
OL,15,Fworked tirelessly to expose criminal
OL,16,Fwrongdoing and injustice, helping to
OL,17,Fdrive important and lasting changes in
OL,18,Fthe law.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
