CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1781633474
OL,3,CITV legend and Cook Report journalist
OL,4,CRoger Cook dies aged 83
OL,6,F"His fearless contribution to
OL,7,Fjournalism will long be remembered,
OL,8,Fand we send our deepest sympathies and
OL,9,Fcondolences to his wife, family and
OL,10,Ffriends at this difficult time".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
